      <td width="50%" style="padding:20px; padding-bottom:0px;"><strong>At Iatric Data we have a new idea about online panels: focus, focus, focus.</strong> Health &amp; Wellness research is our first, middle and last name. When our panelists join via double opt-in, they know that they are going to participate in health &amp; wellness research studies. Through a series of detailed profiling questionnaires and our proprietary model, <strong>PrognoStat<sup>SM</sup></strong>, we provide the most reliable sample in the industry. When you're looking for asthmatics, we deliver asthmatics.</td>
      <td width="50%" style="padding:20px; padding-bottom:0px;">Via our website www.MyHealthOpinion.com, we build a committed relationship with our panelists. There they have access to health &amp; wellness information, guides, assessments, news and feature articles. Strict panel management rules and monthly respondent sweepstakes featuring health &amp; wellness prizes ensure that our panelists are not 'clicking-for-points.' We strive to have the lowest drop-off rate in the industry, resulting in the ability to conduct cost-effective longitudinal studies.</td>
